OL,8,CStage B
OL,10,GVoice assistants are getting easier to
OL,11,Gdeploy, but they’re still generic.
OL,12,GThis talk follows my attempt to build
OL,13,Ga mostly-local Home Assistant voice
OL,14,Gsystem that not only controls the
OL,15,Ghouse, but has a personality. We’ll
OL,16,Gexplore the trade-offs between local
OL,17,Gand cloud services, improving
OL,18,Grecognition for regional accents,
OL,19,Gcreating custom Piper voices, and
OL,20,Gadding character to an assistant that
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
